    "Prior research has raised serious concerns about the ability of LMs to generalize their reasoning or adapt to specialized domains (Bender et al., 2021; Kocoń et al., 2023), particularly finance Kang and Liu, 2023; Zhao et al., 2024; Dong et al., 2024; Chen et al., 2024.",
    "Despite this explosion of interest and skepticism, there has not yet been a sufficiently rigorous and holistic evaluation of the performance of foundation LMs for core NLP tasks in finance.",
